Hillary Clinton reactivated her  Twitter account  this week. Writer Yoni Brenner ( @yonibrenner ) catches up with other famous Americans on Twitter.  (Photos: Getty Images; Illustrations: Bloomberg View) 1. Benjamin Franklin 2. Thomas Jefferson   3. Thomas Paine 4. Abigail Adams   5. Lewis & Clark 6. Davy Crockett 7. Abraham Lincoln   8. Jefferson Davis   9. George Armstrong Custer 10. William McKinley 11. Franklin Delano Roosevelt 12. Richard Nixon   13. Jimmy Carter   14. Ronald Reagan (Yoni Brenner is a writer for film, television and print. He is a frequent contributor to the New Yorker.)